@api = http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### GET a avatar by ID
GET {{api}}/avatar/#id


### GET  multiple avatars
GET {{api}}/avatars/


### Create Avatar
POST {{api}}/avatar/new/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "algo",
    "url": "url.com",
    "description": "jnakjndjkad"
}


### Update Avatar
PUT {{api}}/avatar/update/#id
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "algo tambie",
    "url": "otraurl.com",
    "description": "otra desc"
}


### DELETE avatar
DELETE {{api}}/avatar/delete/#id